  "description": "Translate Remaining Polish Language Strings in pl/programs Module\n\nComplete the Polish language translation for the pl/programs module, which currently contains untranslated strings in English or other languages.\n\nRequirements:\n- Identify all untranslated strings within the pl/programs module\n- Translate missing strings to Polish while maintaining consistent terminology with existing translations\n- Ensure translations fit within UI constraints (button labels, tooltips, etc.)\n- Verify proper handling of Polish special characters (ą, ć, ę, ł, ń, ó, ś, ź, ż)\n- Check for plural forms and ensure correct Polish grammatical cases are used\n- Test the interface with translated strings to confirm proper display\n- Maintain translation key structure and formatting from the source files\n\nEdge cases to consider:\n- Technical terms that may not have direct Polish equivalents\n- String interpolation and variable placeholders\n- Context-dependent translations where same English word needs different Polish translations\n- Character length differences between English and Polish affecting layout",
